snippet.title: Isle of Jura - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1703140/Isle_of_Jura/

Releasing in January 2022. Take a fishing trip to Jura, a remote and beautiful island. Explore, meet the locals, and catch delicious fish!
